column2: SELECT INTO MyDB.photo_vdl_#   L.cID, SPO.specObjID, SPO.ra, SPO.dec, SPO.z,    SPO.modelMag_u, SPO.modelMag_g, SPO.modelMag_r, SPO.modelMag_i, SPO.modelMag_z FROM MyDB.vdL_# as L   OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbySpecObjEq(L.RAJ2#, L.DEJ2#, L.aperture) as SO   INNER JOIN SpecPhotoAll as SPO on SPO.SpecObjID = SO.SpecObjID WHERE SPO.class = &&& and abs(SPO.z - L.z) < # * sqrt(#) * L.sigma
